## 2. Remove the global `gap: 40px`

Your `.left-content` currently has:

```css
gap: 40px;
```

That creates the oversized spaces visible between the heading, subtitle, body, form, and button.

Replace the complete block with:

```css
.left-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    width: 100%;
    padding: clamp(40px, 7vh, 72px) clamp(24px, 7vw, 140px);
}
```

Do not use `gap` here. Control spacing with margins on the individual elements.

