## 6. Remove the old `.confirm-btn` block

Your file still contains an older button block using:

```css
background: #073331;
padding: 0 24px;
font-weight: 700;
gap: 8px;
margin-top: 40px;
```

That old rule conflicts with the newer design rule.

Delete or fully comment out the older `.confirm-btn` declaration and retain only this:

```css
.confirm-btn {
    min-width: 138px;
    height: 48px;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--color-green-light);
    border-radius: 1000px;
